unisDot11APMtIntfStaDetected NOTIFICATION-TYPE
    OBJECTS
        {
            unisDot11Channel,
            unisDot11APIntfDevMACAddress
        }
    STATUS current
    DESCRIPTION
        "The notification will be sent when some ambient station interferes with
